Migrate

User List

The list of users being migrated.

Schedule

You can schedule via the Windows Task Scheduler.

Provisioning

You can set the password and Class of Service for unprovisioned users. Unprovisioned users will appear with a greyed out icon in the Users listbox.

Preview

Hit this button to do a test run. Nothing will be migrated to the Zimbra server.

Migrate

Hit this button to begin the Migration. You will be moved to the Results view, where you can view statistics for individual user migrations.
